{
  "stem": "22047.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I-- I guess it's funny how you become what-- in some people's minds you're a hero.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't think of myself as a hero at all at the time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I asked my bazooka man to fire off a shot down-- I could see these bunkers that we were getting fire from.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he fired off a shot and it hit near one of these bunkers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I saw these Germans jump out of the bunker and go run down to another place.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I said, let's go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I got up and all my troops and we ran down this hill and captured that particular area.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We caught, oh, about 15 German prisoners.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And for that, I was awarded the Silver Star.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I guess you saw that thing in the book.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You know, I didn't think of myself as a hero at all or anybody that should have been awarded a medal, because I was getting tired of sitting on the side of this hill being shot at.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And if there's a chance that I can capture them before they get ready, I should do it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Get up and go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "This isn't winning a war, sitting here on the side of a hill.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So we went down and captured these folks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then we started to proceed and we ran into some snipers that-- that killed one of my machine gunners and his-- his ammunition bearer.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And so we neutralized them and then really started our move toward the Siegfried Line.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And that was an interesting situation, going up these steep mountains, in the Harz range of mountains.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We were so tired by the time we got halfway up these mountains that we'd hardly move.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
